description:
Includes 10 arranged songs from "Touhou Koumakyou," "Touhou Youyoumu," and "Touhou Eiyashou" as additional download contents for "Groove Coaster Wai Wai Party !!!!".

Also includes navigators (with voice) of Cirno and Scarlet Police (a set of Remilia, Sakuya, Patchouli) and avatars.

This pack includes the following content.
■Songs Pack (10 songs)
・Scarlet Police Getto Patrol 24 hour / Shichijo Lettuce Group
・No Life Queen [DJ Command Remix] / SOUND HOLIC Vs. Eurobeat Union feat. Nana Takahashi
・Who Killed U.N.Owen / Liz Triangle
・Hosoi sen / TaNaBaTa
・Touhou Sangakusai / COSIO
・Feast of the Boundary / MASAKI feat. Yukari Yakumo(CV:Shizuka Ito) (from 「Touhou Spell Bubble」) *Locked
・Ttewi -Eientewi ver.- / SEKKENYA
・Kanbu de Tomatte sugu Tokeru Kyoki no Udongein / ARM (IOSYS)
・Cruel Moon NuMIX / TatshMusicCircle
・Kakoi naki yo ha ichigo no tsukikage / BUTAOTOME

■Navigators
・CIRNO(Scarlet Police) *with voice(CV:miko)
・Scarlet Police *with voice(CV:Kokon Koko, 96, Iwasugi Natsu)

■Avatars
・EIRIN(2D)
・KAGUYA(2D)
・REMILIA(SP,2D)
・SAKUYA(SP,2D)
・PATCHOULI(SP,2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Touhou Project Arrangements Pack 7
